        ## Package for Release
        
        To prepare this tool for release a script has been prepared.
        
        ```
        (env) user@host:~/sln_imx_rt_prog_and_test $ deactivate # Deactivate the virtual environment
        
        user@host:~/sln_imx_rt_prog_and_test $ python3 prep_for_release.py sln_alexa_iot
        supported platforms: sln_alexa_iot, sln_local2_iot, sln_vizn_iot, sln_viznas_iot
        user@host:~/sln_imx_rt_prog_and_test $ python prep_for_release.py [PLATFORM]
        SUCCESS: Created release directory.
        SUCCESS: Docs copied.
        SUCCESS: Default image binary copied.
        SUCCESS: Ivaldi source copied.
        SUCCESS: Readme copied.
        SUCCESS: Readme copied.
        SUCCESS: Default scripts copied.
        SUCCESS: Tools copied.
        SUCCESS: Copied CA folder.
        SUCCESS: Top level gitignore copied.
        SUCCESS: Readme copied.
        SUCCESS: Requirements file copied.
        ```
        
        Once the script has run there will be a .zip archive in the current directory. The .zip file name will match the following format.
        
        ```
        Ivaldi_[PLATFORM]_mmdd_hhmmss.zip
        ```
        
        For example, the following file was built for sln_alexa_iot platform on 03/21 at 15:28:47:
        
        ```
        Ivaldi_sln_alexa_iot_0321_152847.zip
        ```
        
